def KNN(X,Y,test_point,k=5):
    m=X.shape[0]
    vals=[]
    for i in range(m):
        d=dist(test_point,X[i])
        vals.append((d,Y[i]))
    vals=sorted(vals)
    vals=np.array(vals[:k])
    #print(vals)
    b=(np.unique(vals[:,1],return_counts=True))
    idx=np.argmax(b[1])
    pred=b[0][idx]
    return int(pred)
